  # Issue X3-35454 - 2017-05-03 by FGR : END
  Sorta [M:CBW2]NBCLL [M:CBW2]NBCLL Order By [M:CBW2]CLLFIEPOS(indice), [M:CBW2]CLLFIECOD(indice)
  # Issue X3-35454 - 2017-05-03 by FGR : BEGIN
